text: Love this stall beehoon. Even though the portion have shrunk.

The hawker dropped the chicken wing on the table, didn’t give me the complete item and still dare to charge me in full price. When I question her, she just take the same piece of meat from the table and put on food.  Lesson learned, don’t pay this kind of hawker until you are happy with the food that was served.
